Just do

$ repo init -u https://github.com/HtcLegacy/manifests.git -b lollipop

then

$ repo sync -f --no-clone-bundle

Run updates.sh from /vendor/LegacyXperiaAOSP/extras before build and apply this change manually https://github.com/CyanogenMod/android_external_chromium_org/commit/faebc79552c8867295203c88d804c1f56c39114c (I will add it to repo ASAP). This one needs to be reverted in android_build to fix boot: https://github.com/CyanogenMod/android_build/commit/4b86ea582b77fc2bd8a0811b5af7ada28a0b59fb 
Material MMS app needs some work, use aosp one now

